01:11:21,375 --> 01:11:22,958
Kami di sini! Enyah!

606
01:11:23,042 --> 01:11:24,375
Di sini!

607
01:11:24,458 --> 01:11:27,208
Kau lihat? Dia menyerang suamiku.

608
01:11:27,292 --> 01:11:28,375
Tolong!

609
01:11:28,458 --> 01:11:30,958
Tolong!

